<strong>REFERENCE LIST ENTRY</strong>
<br>
<br>
Add a reference list at the end of your essay citing all sources used in the body of your writing.
<br>
<br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	Author. (Year, month and day of publication). Title of article. 
	<em>Name of Publication</em>, page number(s).
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	<span class="hover" title="Author">Smith, A.</span> 
	(<span class="hover" title="Year, month and day of publication">2056, December 15</span>). 
	<span class="hover" title="Title of article">Something went wrong in plane crash, experts say</span>. 
	<em><span class="hover" title="Name of Publication">Herald Tribune</span></em>, 
	<span class="hover" title="page number">p. A5</span>. 
</blockquote>
